name: JFT Strategies Fund
longDescription: The Fund's investment objective is to maximize return on investment to holders of Unitsholders while seeking to mitigate market risk and volatility Fund invests in an actively managed portfolio of long and short positions in any one or a combination of equities, debt securities or other securities.
